                    </TablixRow>
                    <TablixRow>
                      <Height>1.76417cm</Height>
                      <TablixCells>
                        <TablixCell>
                          <CellContents>
                            <Textbox Name="Textbox382">
                              <CanGrow>true</CanGrow>
                              <KeepTogether>true</KeepTogether>
                              <Paragraphs>
                                <Paragraph>
                                  <TextRuns>
                                    <TextRun>
                                      <Value>Instruction to Mentors</Value>
                                      <Style>
                                        <FontWeight>Bold</FontWeight>
                                      </Style>
                                    </TextRun>
                                  </TextRuns>
                                  <Style>
                                    <TextAlign>Center</TextAlign>
                                  </Style>
                                </Paragraph>
                              </Paragraphs>
                              <rd:DefaultName>Textbox382</rd:DefaultName>
                              <Style>
                                <Border>
                                  <Style>None</Style>
                                </Border>
                                <PaddingLeft>2pt</PaddingLeft>
                                <PaddingRight>2pt</PaddingRight>
                                <PaddingTop>2pt</PaddingTop>
                                <PaddingBottom>2pt</PaddingBottom>
                              </Style>
                            </Textbox>
                            <ColSpan>16</ColSpan>
                          </CellContents>
                        </TablixCell>
                        <TablixCell />
                        <TablixCell />
                        <TablixCell />
                        <TablixCell />
                        <TablixCell />
                        <TablixCell />
                        <TablixCell />
                        <TablixCell />
                        <TablixCell />
                        <TablixCell />
                        <TablixCell />
                        <TablixCell />
                        <TablixCell />
                        <TablixCell />
                        <TablixCell />
                      </TablixCells>
                    </TablixRow>
                    <TablixRow>
                      <Height>5.43306cm</Height>
                      <TablixCells>
                        <TablixCell>
                          <CellContents>
                            <Textbox Name="Textbox396">
                              <CanGrow>true</CanGrow>
                              <KeepTogether>true</KeepTogether>
                              <Paragraphs>
                                <Paragraph>
                                  <TextRuns>
                                    <TextRun>
                                      <Value>• The students assigned to you for mentoring are to be dealt with patience and politeness and the effort should be made to ease the anxiety of the student especially when they are in the first year of their academics.</Value>
                                      <Style>
                                        <FontSize>7pt</FontSize>
                                      </Style>
                                    </TextRun>
                                  </TextRuns>
                                  <Style />
                                </Paragraph>
                                <Paragraph>
                                  <TextRuns>
                                    <TextRun>
                                      <Value>
• When any student approaches you with problems in academics (subject/result etc) please try to support such students, on the bases of their emotional quotient. Try to arrange extra classes or remedial classes for such students by talking him/her to the HOD of the department and, if needed, to the Principal.</Value>
                                      <Style>
                                        <FontSize>7pt</FontSize>
                                      </Style>
                                    </TextRun>
                                  </TextRuns>
                                  <Style />
                                </Paragraph>
                                <Paragraph>
                                  <TextRuns>
                                    <TextRun>
                                      <Value>
• Any personal problem/family problem of the students should be brought to the notice of HOD without fail.</Value>
                                      <Style>
                                        <FontSize>7pt</FontSize>
                                      </Style>
                                    </TextRun>
                                  </TextRuns>
                                  <Style />
                                </Paragraph>
                                <Paragraph>
                                  <TextRuns>
                                    <TextRun>
                                      <Value />
                                      <Style>
                                        <FontSize>7pt</FontSize>
                                      </Style>
                                    </TextRun>
                                  </TextRuns>
                                  <Style />
                                </Paragraph>
                                <Paragraph>
                                  <TextRuns>
                                    <TextRun>
                                      <Value>• Never admonish or get into an argument with students while counselling them. If they misbehave should be brought to the notice of HOD.</Value>
                                      <Style>
                                        <FontSize>7pt</FontSize>
                                      </Style>
                                    </TextRun>
                                  </TextRuns>
                                  <Style />
                                </Paragraph>
                                <Paragraph>
                                  <TextRuns>
                                    <TextRun>
                                      <Value>
• Always try to get the updated information about the candidate and then, make updations in the student's Mentoring Handbook (after due verification of the records presented) and, in no case any erroneous or misleading information should be mentioned in the Mentoring Handbook.</Value>
                                      <Style>
                                        <FontSize>7pt</FontSize>
                                      </Style>
                                    </TextRun>
                                  </TextRuns>
                                  <Style />
                                </Paragraph>
                              </Paragraphs>
                              <rd:DefaultName>Textbox396</rd:DefaultName>
                              <Style>
                                <Border>
                                  <Style>None</Style>
                                </Border>
                                <PaddingLeft>2pt</PaddingLeft>
                                <PaddingRight>2pt</PaddingRight>
                                <PaddingTop>2pt</PaddingTop>
                                <PaddingBottom>2pt</PaddingBottom>
                              </Style>
                            </Textbox>
                            <ColSpan>16</ColSpan>
                          </CellContents>
                        </TablixCell>
