                        <TablixCell>
                          <CellContents>
                            <Textbox Name="Textbox48">
                              <CanGrow>true</CanGrow>
                              <KeepTogether>true</KeepTogether>
                              <Paragraphs>
                                <Paragraph>
                                  <TextRuns>
                                    <TextRun>
                                      <Value>• Implementing a student mentoring scheme cultivates positive community relations and contributes to local and regional economic growth objectives.

• Students' motivation and aspirations will increase, positively impacting morale within the learning community.

• Mentoring will optimize the achievements of both individual students and groups who may be at risk of underperforming, thereby eliminating barriers to success for vulnerable student populations.

• Mentoring programs enhance the skills of both staff and students, leading to improved student attendance and higher retention rates.</Value>
                                      <Style>
                                        <FontSize>7pt</FontSize>
                                      </Style>
                                    </TextRun>
                                  </TextRuns>
                                  <Style />
                                </Paragraph>
